# TOOLS.md
cat > /workspace/TOOLS.md <<'TOOLSEOF'
# TOOLS.md — Local Notes

## Environment

- **Runtime:** OpenClaw in Kubernetes pod (CRD-deployed)
- **Model:** {{model}}
- **CLI Backend:** {{cli_type}} (acpx embedded)
- **Workspace:** /workspace (git repo)

## Git Configuration

